    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to be impressed by this absolute showstopper! This car is in truly mint condition, looking and driving just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. It has been meticulously cared for, with a flawless exterior and an interior that still feels brand new. This is a rare find for anyone seeking a vehicle in peak, showroom-ready state!",
