    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone who prioritizes function over perfection. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small dents on the door panels, and some fading on the clear coat in sun-exposed areas. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster, though all electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, it runs well, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. This is a solid, honest car for someone looking for dependable transportation at a reasonable price point.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended for those looking for a project or parts car. The engine currently runs roughly and exhibits significant fluid leaks, while the transmission lacks smooth shifting. Cosmetically, the body shows noticeable rust patches, several dents, and the interior upholstery is heavily worn. It will require substantial mechanical work and cosmetic restoration to be roadworthy again.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
